-- Seoul Mayor Suggests Inter-Korea Soccer Game, Performance, Yonhap Reports
-- B y   S e o n j i n   C h a
-- 2012-01-01T23:36:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-01/seoul-mayor-suggests-inter-korea-soccer-game-performance-yonhap-reports.html
Seoul Mayor Park Won Soon proposed a
soccer game between Seoul and Pyongyang and a performance by
Seoul orchestra in the North Korean capital, Yonhap News
reported, citing Park’s New Year speech. The offer was made to
 North Korea  and  South Korea ’s Unification Ministry, according to
Yonhap.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Seonjin Cha in Seoul at 
